  <brief_title>Dental Health Epidemiology Among Israel Defense Forces (IDF) Recruits</brief_title>
  <official_title>Caries, Gingivitis, Dental Trauma and Fluorosis Prevalence Among IDF Recruits - an Epidemiological Survey</official_title>
